<HEADLINE> CPPCC Standing Committee Held Meeting in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 22 (Xinhua) -- The 22nd meeting of the
Standing Committee of the National Committee of the Chinese
People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) was held here
today, placing the study and implementation of the essence of the
15th National Congress of the Communist Party of China at the top
of the agenda.
</P>
<P>
Li Ruihuan, member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and chairman of the CPPCC
National Committee, presided over the meeting and delivered an
important speech.
</P>
<P>
Wen Jiabao, member of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central
Committee and member of the Secretariat of the CPC Central
Committee, briefed participants on the essence of the 15th CPC
National Congress, entrusted by the CPC Central Committee.
</P>
<P>
The 15th Party National Congress was very successful, concluded
Wen, adding that Jiang Zemin's report is a political declaration
and call to action for people to forge ahead into the new century.
</P>
<P>
He said the first Plenary Session of the 15th CPC Central
Committee elected the new central leading body with Jiang Zemin as
its core.
</P>
<P>
The most import work at present is to study and implement the
fundamental issues of the congress, unify the thinking of the whole
party, and gather the strength of the entire nation to realize
various tasks assigned by the congress, he noted.
</P>
<P>
Addressing the meeting, Li Ruihuan said the congress, with the
theme of holding high the banner of the Deng Xiaoping Theory for
an overall advancement of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics into the 21st century, drew up a comprehensive
plan for China's reform, opening-up and socialist modernization
drive.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's report is a pragmatic document to guide the CPPCC work,
and the CPPCC bodies at all levels must regard the study and
implementation of the essence of the congress as an important task
now and in the future, he pointed out.
</P>
<P>
Li emphasized that CPPCC bodies at all levels must summarize
their work over the past years and also direct their future work,
especially the reshuffling of the CPPCC, based on the guiding
theme of the congress, to lay a sound basis for the CPPCC of the
new term. 
</P>
