<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Vice-Premier Zhu Rongji
said here today that Hong Kong serves as an important converging
point between the economy of China and that of the world.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a World Bank seminar here today, Zhu said that
since its return to China over two months ago, the government of
the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) has been
operating smoothly, giving full expression to the principles of
