stability of Hong Kong not only serves the fundamental interests
of Hong Kong, but also benefits the economic development of
China's mainland and that of East Asia and the world at large.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong, as an important international financial, trade,
shipping, tourism and information center, will certainly play a
more active role in developing economic and trade ties between
China and other countries in the world, Zhu said. 
</P>
