deepen mutual understanding and promote the existing friendly
cooperation between the two countries and their armed forces.
</P>
<P>
He stressed the Chinese side has consistently attached
significance to its cooperation and military ties with the
Gabonese.
</P>
<P>
He also extended his appreciation to the Gabonese Government
for its "one China" stand.
</P>
<P>
