recent years, the cooperation of friendship between the two
countries has grown steadily.
</P>
<P>
He said Gabon, as a good friend of China, will not change its
policies toward China. No country in the world could sever Gabon's
friendly relationship with China, he added.
</P>
<P>
He expressed his satisfaction with the sound development of
Gabonese-Chinese military ties and hoped they could be further
tightened.
</P>
<P>
Prior to the talks, Chi hosted a welcoming ceremony for Ngari
and his party, who arrived here yesterday as guests of Chi.
</P>
