at district and sub-district headquarters on September 23 and
rallies and torch processions across the country on September 24.
</P>
<P>
Khaleda Zia said that her party had no alternative but to call
a hartal for what the government had unleashed a "reign of terror
and repression" to suppress the opposition movement.
</P>
<P>
She called upon people from all walks of life to make the
hartal program a success.  
