<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, September 22 (Xinhua) -- At least 10 people were killed
and more than 100 others injured in a collision of commuter trains
this morning in the Southern Manila suburb, police said.
</P>
<P>
Police said a speedy train was on way to Manila when its end
coach accidentally detached from the rest hitting the following
train along the railroad track in Buli Muntinlupa city, south of
Manila.
</P>
<P>
