In the early matches, Pete Sampras beat Mark Philippoussis and
Micheal Chang outplayed Pat Rafter.
</P>
<P>
The Australians scored the sole point in the doubles match as
Todd Woodbridge and Mark Woodforde defeated Sampras and Todd
Martin.
</P>
<P>
The Americans will be aiming for their 32nd Davis Cup against
five-time champions Sweden slated for November. 
